Hey, the ads got rejected, I don't agree with that? What is the reason again?

Hey there! Ad rejection reasons can vary, but you should have received an email from Ad Support with the specific reason for your ad's rejection. If you believe your ad complies with the policies or if the rejection was a misunderstanding, you can submit an appeal by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. For more details on what to do next, check out this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). Let me know if you need further assistance!
